1
00:00:21,890 --> 00:00:28,140
♪ Shout it out loud,
I don't want to part with you ♪

2
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:34,470
♪ Shout it out loud,
I love my hometown and you ♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:37,430
Son,

4
00:00:40,900 --> 00:00:42,860
I can't be with you as you grow up.

5
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:49,000
This is a beautiful world.

6
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,580
You must go see it.

7
00:00:59,330 --> 00:01:01,120
Cherish the people around you.

8
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,210
[OOPS! I'M IN JAIL]

9
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:48,370
[Episode 12]

10
00:02:48,370 --> 00:02:49,750
Come on in.

11
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,370
This way.

12
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,180
Drop the tailgate, will you?

13
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:58,050
You guys have checked twice.

14
00:02:58,260 --> 00:03:00,220
I need to check the slop buckets.

15
00:03:00,220 --> 00:03:01,880
What happened?

16
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,050
Checking for so long.

17
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:05,130
A prisoner has gone missing.

18
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,300
At this rate, Wa won't be able to get out.

19
00:03:07,300 --> 00:03:09,630
We must do something—let's create chaos.

20
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,550
Chaos?

21
00:03:12,050 --> 00:03:13,050
How?

22
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:16,010
Set a fire.

23
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,040
It's windy today.

24
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:24,460
The fire will spread.

25
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:28,560
A prisoner is missing.

26
00:03:28,790 --> 00:03:29,380
What?

27
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,340
You think he was chopped up

28
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:32,000
and placed in my slop buckets?

29
00:03:32,450 --> 00:03:34,910
What kind of movies do you watch?

30
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:37,420
Not the kind
that includes a plot like this.

31
00:03:37,630 --> 00:03:38,300
Got it.

32
00:03:45,050 --> 00:03:46,510
Why is the fire alarm on?

33
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:55,300
Wait here for a moment.

34
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,260
-I'll be right back.
-Are you done with the check?

35
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:58,630
No. It's not finished yet.

36
00:03:58,630 --> 00:03:59,130
Please.

37
00:03:59,130 --> 00:04:00,300
Just wait a minute. It's not done yet.

38
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:01,930
Be cooperative. The superiors have ordered
a thorough inspection.

39
00:04:01,930 --> 00:04:02,680
This check isn't finished.

40
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,680
Just wait for me to come back.

41
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:05,180
I'll go find out what's happening.

42
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,760
What is this about?

43
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,820
Why is the fire alarm going off today?

44
00:04:08,970 --> 00:04:10,430
Well, it's just...

45
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:12,050
A small fire might have

46
00:04:12,050 --> 00:04:14,010
happened somewhere.

47
00:04:14,010 --> 00:04:14,760
What?

48
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,680
Don't worry.
It'll be taken care of. Rest assured.

49
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,300
Fix it now!

50
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,380
Yes, sure.

51
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,300
All is fine.

52
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:21,130
This is probably a false alarm.

53
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,880
Jiang Yijie, Shui,

54
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:25,430
why is the alarm going off?

55
00:04:25,550 --> 00:04:27,050
Chief Hu, I hear you. I'm on it.

56
00:04:27,050 --> 00:04:27,760
I'm handling it.

57
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,560
Shun, where exactly is the fire?

58
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,550
Chief Hu,

59
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:33,980
it's in the mess hall.

60
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,050
Put it out now.

61
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:37,800
Or you'll all be dead meat!

62
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,970
-Shun!
-Shui will cover for me.

63
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:41,470
Okay.

64
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:43,550
The mess hall...

65
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,370
Shui, guard the vehicle check-up point.

66
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:47,680
This is a diversionary tactic.

67
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,630
Guard the vehicle check-up point!

68
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:50,300
The cells must be kept from fire.

69
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,880
I'll go handle the problem now.

70
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,880
Do not leave the vehicle check-up point.
I'm on my way!

71
00:04:58,130 --> 00:04:58,930
Shui!

72
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:03,550
Shui, stay put!

73
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,940
Not one bucket was properly covered.

74
00:05:21,470 --> 00:05:23,500
All is fine. The alarm will stop soon.

75
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,200
Everything is fine, Sir.

76
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:28,470
Is that them?

77
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,050
What should we do now?

78
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,730
Wang Zhongwen, what are you doing?

79
00:05:43,780 --> 00:05:44,370
What should we do at this moment?

80
00:05:44,370 --> 00:05:46,870
[Vehicle Check-up Point]

81
00:05:54,970 --> 00:05:57,470
What's going on? Nobody's around.

82
00:06:07,010 --> 00:06:08,050
No, we can't do this.

83
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:09,100
We'll all be arrested

84
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,740
once this button is pressed.

85
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:11,290
We can't do it.

86
00:06:11,290 --> 00:06:13,350
Or Yijie will have all of us arrested.

87
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,930
We're done for!

88
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,930
Bye bye!

89
00:06:36,180 --> 00:06:37,760
We're finished.
How long will we be kept in jail for this?

90
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,620
This carries a 10-year sentence.

91
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,450
Central Desk, open the gate
to the vehicle check-up point.

92
00:06:46,450 --> 00:06:49,710
Central Desk, open the gate
to the vehicle check-up point!

93
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,130
Gao Zhiyao!

94
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,630
We made it.

95
00:07:53,590 --> 00:07:54,850
Wa, what are you doing?

96
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,590
Keep a lower profile.

97
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:00,700
This is too conspicuous.

98
00:08:33,179 --> 00:08:34,049
Stop the truck!

99
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,950
Gao Zhiyao!

100
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:37,510
Pull over!

101
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,700
It's the devil!

102
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,630
Inmate 9568!

103
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:51,120
Stop the truck!

104
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,680
Why is he pulling over?

105
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:58,380
Why stop the truck?

106
00:08:58,380 --> 00:09:00,800
This is odd. I just went
and now I have to go again. Gosh.

107
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:01,930
Gao Zhiyao!

108
00:09:02,490 --> 00:09:03,900
You bastard!

109
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:07,460
Get off the truck now.

110
00:09:14,380 --> 00:09:15,040
I forgot...

111
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,760
the toilet paper!

112
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:22,220
My toilet paper...

113
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:23,430
Who are you?

114
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:23,930
Zhang Longji!

115
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:25,010
Get in!

116
00:09:25,380 --> 00:09:26,180
Wait a moment!

117
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:27,760
Wa, drive!

118
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,180
-Be quiet!
-He's coming for us!

119
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,380
Wa, where's this stink from?

120
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,760
The devil's catching up!

121
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,760
Hurry!

122
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,220
Get out!

123
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:35,090
Everyone out!

124
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:36,050
Wait!

125
00:09:36,050 --> 00:09:36,880
Don't make me tase you!

126
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,380
Listen to me,

127
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:38,090
this stuff is dangerous!

128
00:09:38,090 --> 00:09:38,750
Get out now!

129
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,470
See? This keeps happening!

130
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:48,010
He got hurt. You're the worst! The worst!

131
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:48,930
Get out!

132
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:51,020
Everyone out!

133
00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:52,920
I'm not joking with you!

134
00:09:53,260 --> 00:09:54,050
Everyone, get out!

135
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:55,380
Gao Zhiyao, get out now!

136
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:57,180
Calm down!

137
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,540
We're just going out for a bit.

138
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,000
We'll only be gone for a moment.

139
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,180
We'll go back to the prison.

140
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:02,880
Get out, slowly.

141
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,630
Wa!

142
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:04,630
Wa, run!

143
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:05,600
Gao Zhiyao...

144
00:10:07,130 --> 00:10:08,010
Zhang Longji!

145
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:16,500
Whose side are you on?

146
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:19,550
Come here!

147
00:10:20,010 --> 00:10:20,630
Wa!

148
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,720
Come back!

149
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,180
Senior!

150
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,680
-Senior...
-Gao Zhiyao...

151
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,570
I'm sorry, Senior.

152
00:10:27,570 --> 00:10:29,020
He'll be back soon.

153
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,030
I'm sorry.

154
00:10:31,640 --> 00:10:32,470
Senior...

155
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,260
You bummer...

156
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,240
Don't!

157
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:52,250
Senior, can't you make an exception?

158
00:10:52,250 --> 00:10:53,910
Can't you show some humanity?

159
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:55,790
What are you saying?

160
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,900
You're helping with a prison break
as a law enforcer.

161
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:59,230
Are you out of your mind?

162
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:00,920
The keys...

163
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:03,970
Senior...

164
00:11:04,670 --> 00:11:05,930
He just wants to see his son

165
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:07,130
before he dies.

166
00:11:07,130 --> 00:11:08,480
Can you live with yourself for denying him

167
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,800
what may be the last chance
to see his son?

168
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:11,800
But this is not the right way to help him!

169
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:12,800
You're assisting in a prison break

170
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,600
as a law enforcer. Are you crazy?

171
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:25,330
The keys.

172
00:11:25,350 --> 00:11:26,810
Give me the keys!

173
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:29,180
Break!

174
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,780
To hell with your damn system!

175
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:43,860
Are you crazy?

176
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,430
You tased me twice.

177
00:11:57,430 --> 00:11:59,380
Who do you think you are, Pikachu?

178
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:00,130
Senior.

179
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,380
Senior!

180
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:02,630
Pika pika.

181
00:12:06,010 --> 00:12:06,760
Senior.

182
00:12:07,130 --> 00:12:07,880
Senior!

183
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:17,260
Honey.

184
00:12:17,590 --> 00:12:19,050
Where are you, Chihuahua?

185
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,240
There was a minor hiccup.

186
00:12:21,930 --> 00:12:23,060
But I made my way out.

187
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:25,880
Then just steal a car and run away.

188
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:26,840
Don't come to us.

189
00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:32,910
Zhang Longji, are you listening?

190
00:12:34,630 --> 00:12:35,630
Boss,

191
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:37,560
you can't just break out of prison.

192
00:12:38,130 --> 00:12:39,260
This is a crime.

193
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,980
I'll be put in jail too.

194
00:12:41,180 --> 00:12:42,510
If anything goes wrong,

195
00:12:42,590 --> 00:12:43,280
I'll take full responsibility.

196
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:45,210
Will you really take all the blame?

197
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,510
I'll help you.

198
00:12:49,690 --> 00:12:51,290
But you must promise me one thing.

199
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:52,890
You must come back right away

200
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,280
after you hold your son.

201
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,050
Easy with the noodles.

202
00:12:58,050 --> 00:12:58,840
Zhang Longji, listen.

203
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,880
No more hesitation.

204
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,430
Just steal a car and run away.

205
00:13:01,430 --> 00:13:02,180
Listen to me.

206
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:02,840
No way.

207
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,430
-Listen to me!
-If you get caught,

208
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:05,160
you'll never see your son!

209
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:07,110
I'll go with the original plan.

210
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,380
I'm coming to see you.

211
00:13:09,930 --> 00:13:10,880
Are you crazy?

212
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:13,010
-That's it.
-Why don't you just leave?

213
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,930
To think I even personally

214
00:13:33,930 --> 00:13:36,130
handed you the security plan for today.

215
00:13:36,180 --> 00:13:38,200
Senior, you did a good job on that plan.

216
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:40,260
We nearly failed to leave the prison.

217
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:44,180
Inmate 9568 had better come back.

218
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:46,300
Or you'll be thrown into jail.

219
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,630
If that happens, I'll tell the media

220
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:50,460
that you guys deny treatment
to an inmate with cancer!

221
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:52,210
I've told you I am trying.

222
00:13:52,230 --> 00:13:54,110
He would be dead
by the time you work out something.

223
00:13:54,110 --> 00:13:55,280
Enough!

224
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,390
Stop arguing.

225
00:13:56,410 --> 00:13:58,800
You'll both be finished
if I tell the media about this,

226
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,730
especially you.

227
00:14:00,010 --> 00:14:02,630
You handcuffed me and even tased me.

228
00:14:02,630 --> 00:14:04,830
What did I do wrong? Did I commit a crime?

229
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,220
You just assaulted an officer!

230
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:07,620
You tased me a moment ago.

231
00:14:07,930 --> 00:14:09,260
But you tased me twice!

232
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,800
I'm only a slop collector.
What have I done wrong?

233
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:14,590
What has an ordinary civilian
such as myself done wrong?

234
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:15,260
Exactly!

235
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:29,160
You made this happen,
since you just tased me.

236
00:14:57,380 --> 00:14:58,760
It's been a long time.

237
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:01,130
Why aren't they here yet?

238
00:15:03,220 --> 00:15:05,020
Could something have happened?

239
00:15:51,180 --> 00:15:51,980
My apologies.

240
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,050
Senior.

241
00:16:22,490 --> 00:16:23,890
Why are you guys here too?

242
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:29,780
You're all in this together?

243
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:37,240
They have nothing to do with this.

244
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:40,590
I planned for this whole thing.

245
00:16:40,590 --> 00:16:41,840
-Wa...
-Why didn't you run as I told you?

246
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,440
Everyone stay where you are!

247
00:16:44,430 --> 00:16:45,160
Inmate 9568.

248
00:16:46,010 --> 00:16:46,740
Stop moving.

249
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,690
I'm too tired

250
00:16:49,050 --> 00:16:50,050
to run anymore.

251
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:01,240
Senior.

252
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,730
Alright. There, there.

253
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:04,290
Mom's here.

254
00:17:07,130 --> 00:17:07,880
Senior.

255
00:17:10,589 --> 00:17:13,050
As I said, I won't let you take the blame.

256
00:17:14,230 --> 00:17:16,829
Senior, I'll resign
as soon as I get back to the office.

257
00:17:16,829 --> 00:17:17,520
His son's right there.

258
00:17:17,520 --> 00:17:18,550
Please let him hold his son.

259
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:20,670
Yeah, Senior, don't do this.

260
00:17:24,260 --> 00:17:26,680
Make an exception. Let him see his son.

261
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,780
My son is crying.

262
00:17:29,630 --> 00:17:31,690
Given his current health condition,

263
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:32,930
this could be the last time

264
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:34,330
he gets to hold his child.

265
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:38,050
Let me see my son.

266
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:39,340
I...

267
00:17:40,010 --> 00:17:40,630
Yijie.

268
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:46,630
He's already here. Let him hold his son.

269
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:48,200
Why are you here too?

270
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:50,840
So you've known this all along?

271
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:52,930
Are all of you crazy?

272
00:17:52,930 --> 00:17:54,310
Assisting in a prison break?

273
00:17:54,310 --> 00:17:56,330
I told you this is all my doing.

274
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,240
They're completely innocent!

275
00:17:59,130 --> 00:17:59,630
My...

276
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:00,780
My son is crying.

277
00:18:00,780 --> 00:18:02,130
Please let me see him.

278
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:04,510
Then take me back to the prison, okay?

279
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:06,260
Senior,

280
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:08,150
please show some leniency.

281
00:18:09,050 --> 00:18:10,880
Yeah. Senior, please.

282
00:18:13,510 --> 00:18:14,180
Inmate 9568!

283
00:18:14,180 --> 00:18:15,010
Senior, just a small exception.

284
