565
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:36,180
Where is Gao Zhiyao?

566
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:39,230
Zhiyao said he was tired today
and he'd come next time.

567
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:40,190
Why?

568
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:42,550
How tired is he
that he can't even come see us?

569
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,680
It's quite exhausting
to be an assistant trainer.

570
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:46,550
I once visited him
during a training session.

571
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:48,350
-He seemed happy.
-Here you are.

572
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:49,300
-Thank you.
-It's hot.

573
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:51,430
Does he want to attend contests again?

574
00:33:51,430 --> 00:33:53,230
Of course he'd love to, if he can.

575
00:33:53,430 --> 00:33:55,680
But... it's not his decision to make.

576
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:57,680
Isn't the Custody Division short-staffed?

577
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,800
Why not get Zhiyao back?

578
00:33:58,800 --> 00:34:00,050
How's that possible?

579
00:34:00,430 --> 00:34:02,090
He assisted in a prison break.

580
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,430
Drop that subject for good.

581
00:34:06,430 --> 00:34:08,429
Or we might all get arrested.

582
00:34:08,429 --> 00:34:09,179
No, that won't happen.

583
00:34:09,179 --> 00:34:10,800
We don't know anything whatsoever.

584
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,340
Come on, drink up.

585
00:34:12,590 --> 00:34:13,850
I need to get this call.

586
00:34:14,429 --> 00:34:16,679
Hey babe, are you off work?

587
00:34:17,350 --> 00:34:18,850
Yeah, everyone's here.

588
00:34:19,179 --> 00:34:19,929
Are you coming over?

589
00:34:19,929 --> 00:34:20,800
Do you know who that is?

590
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:21,510
Who?

591
00:34:21,610 --> 00:34:23,480
Shun from the Custody Division.

592
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:24,960
-Really?
-Shun?

593
00:34:25,139 --> 00:34:26,429
-Is it true?
-Yes.

594
00:34:26,929 --> 00:34:28,550
Come on, faster.

595
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,730
Quicken your pace.

596
00:34:49,690 --> 00:34:51,389
Kai, wait a moment. Take a break.

597
00:34:51,389 --> 00:34:52,909
Coach, sorry, a friend of mine is here.

598
00:34:52,909 --> 00:34:53,790
Excuse me.

599
00:34:54,330 --> 00:34:55,060
Take a break.

600
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,130
What are you doing here?

601
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:58,230
I was passing by.

602
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,550
How's your arm?

603
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:03,050
Good.

604
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:05,540
This junior just won a gold medal.

605
00:35:06,050 --> 00:35:07,430
He has great potential.

606
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:13,560
What about you?

607
00:35:14,110 --> 00:35:16,510
When will you officially attend a contest?

608
00:35:17,180 --> 00:35:18,910
Contests are held all the time.

609
00:35:19,300 --> 00:35:21,550
But to get on the official roster,

610
00:35:21,680 --> 00:35:23,930
I need to practice more.

611
00:35:24,430 --> 00:35:26,560
In fact, I don't know what else I can do.

612
00:35:29,590 --> 00:35:31,090
I heard from Jiajun that you're joining

613
00:35:31,090 --> 00:35:33,000
the Prison Reform Foundation, aren't you?

614
00:35:33,000 --> 00:35:34,860
Senior, you're truly ambitious.

615
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:38,300
I wouldn't put it that way. I just...

616
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:40,110
I talked to my father.

617
00:35:41,090 --> 00:35:41,960
Just like you,

618
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:43,980
I want to do what I really care about.

619
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:52,730
What exactly...

620
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:54,780
did your father do?

621
00:35:56,050 --> 00:35:56,760
My father?

622
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,740
I mean your biological father.

623
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:03,010
Why suddenly bring him up?

624
00:36:04,970 --> 00:36:06,370
Jieyu told me something.

625
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:09,850
Was your father really a murderer?

626
00:36:17,470 --> 00:36:18,730
Yes, he was a murderer.

627
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,510
To survive,
he did all sorts of crimes—

628
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:26,970
stealing, kidnapping, robbery, and fraud.

629
00:36:27,930 --> 00:36:29,930
I just never expected him to receive

630
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:31,980
heavier and heavier penalties.

631
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:34,300
He was sentenced to death

632
00:36:35,010 --> 00:36:36,210
when I was 8 years old.

633
00:36:40,870 --> 00:36:42,240
My father once told me

634
00:36:43,050 --> 00:36:44,130
to be a good person

635
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:45,680
and not to go astray.

636
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:49,290
Take one wrong step,
and there will be no going back.

637
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:52,640
Prison shouldn't be the way it is now.

638
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:54,610
Prison should be where people get help,

639
00:36:54,610 --> 00:36:56,180
earn a second chance at life,

640
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:59,240
and are rehabilitated
for entering the society again.

641
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:03,320
As said by Director Xiao.

642
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:10,550
Anyway,

643
00:37:11,010 --> 00:37:11,880
thank you.

644
00:37:14,470 --> 00:37:17,010
You made me realize that the law is rigid,

645
00:37:17,690 --> 00:37:18,820
but people are not.

646
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:30,420
I came here just to tell you

647
00:37:30,430 --> 00:37:32,840
that the Central Prison
is understaffed now.

648
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,260
So, if you feel like coming back,

649
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,660
you're welcome anytime.

650
00:37:37,300 --> 00:37:39,130
I'm welcome anytime?

651
00:37:39,930 --> 00:37:41,190
Can I really come back?

652
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:42,960
Of course.

653
00:37:43,090 --> 00:37:44,180
I'm just not sure if you'll be locked up,

654
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,780
or the one locking people up.

655
00:37:49,630 --> 00:37:50,880
Just kidding. Well,

656
00:37:52,510 --> 00:37:53,760
everyone misses you.

657
00:37:56,820 --> 00:37:58,080
What? You want to puke?

658
00:37:58,540 --> 00:37:59,500
A little bit.

659
00:38:00,630 --> 00:38:03,690
You're not asking me
to be a double agent again, are you?

660
00:38:04,010 --> 00:38:05,050
Mickey Mouse?

661
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:06,800
He's gone.

662
00:38:10,470 --> 00:38:13,470
Handsome,
your beef noodles with extra beef.

663
00:38:13,470 --> 00:38:14,930
It's perfectly warm.

664
00:38:14,930 --> 00:38:16,220
Neither cold nor hot.

665
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:21,440
Do you want to continue the training,

666
00:38:21,970 --> 00:38:23,470
or become a civil servant?

667
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:26,470
Whatever your decision is,

668
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:28,200
you'll always have my support.

669
00:38:35,470 --> 00:38:38,340
Didn't you say you'd let the prices
reflect your compassion?

670
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:39,860
When did I ever say that?

671
00:38:39,970 --> 00:38:42,090
Twenty is far too small a raise.

672
00:38:42,970 --> 00:38:44,900
Do I look like a bodhisattva to you?

673
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:20,720
Coach,

674
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:23,020
can I have a match with the junior?

675
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:25,660
But he's a gold medalist.

676
00:39:25,930 --> 00:39:27,260
I'd like to give it a try.

677
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:31,980
Senior, I won't hold back.

678
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,220
Let's get serious.

679
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:34,720
Come on.

680
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:50,380
Chief.

681
00:40:00,580 --> 00:40:03,670
[Lin Maowei,
Administrator, Custody Division]

682
00:40:18,610 --> 00:40:21,200
[Gao Zhiyao,
Administrator, Custody Division]

683
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,440
I've been keeping it around.

684
00:40:27,570 --> 00:40:29,360
Welcome to the Central Prison.

685
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:31,480
You're all the best of the best.

686
00:40:31,680 --> 00:40:34,090
Listen,
as you start working in the prison,

687
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:36,720
you've basically
become the same as the inmates—

688
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:38,290
you must obey

689
00:40:38,310 --> 00:40:40,220
the superiors' orders unconditionally.

690
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:41,300
The only difference

691
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:43,800
lies in your uniform and ID badges.

692
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:45,680
Don't you dare lose them,

693
00:40:46,050 --> 00:40:47,720
or cause me any trouble.

694
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,070
Yes, Director.

695
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:50,340
Louder!

696
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,050
Yes, Director!

697
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,470
Zhongwen,

698
00:40:53,770 --> 00:40:55,480
your first task today

699
00:40:55,510 --> 00:40:58,430
is to give the prisoners
who were just transferred here

700
00:40:58,430 --> 00:40:59,550
body searches!

701
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:05,300
Move a bit to the left.

702
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:06,810
A bit more, Momo.

703
00:41:06,830 --> 00:41:08,210
I think you should just

704
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:09,650
freestyle.

705
00:41:11,300 --> 00:41:12,800
You are all overestimating actors.

706
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,050
Freestyle in every situation.

707
00:41:14,050 --> 00:41:15,260
Freestyle in dancing too.

708
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:15,980
All of us are asked to...

709
00:41:15,980 --> 00:41:18,370
[Hey, freestyle even in dancing]

710
00:43:46,360 --> 00:43:47,260
Where were you going?

711
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,810
The chair just slid away.
